\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n神又你,    鬼又你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc75de87c2953bdb4fac39d0248f5bba6cedb8e9","tid":209558,"uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:01:45.000Z","msg":"所以其實左行右企先唔會壞<br />\n宜家d力去曬右邊 好快金屬疲勞"},{"pid":"514eda92406aed88183c67c5d7f35804cb057fc7","tid":209558,"uid":1437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有調景嶺hkdi個條梯</blockquote><br />\n個條我有行，megabox就唔敢行"},{"pid":"7f6f848151483283095f1fecdcbde7de4a04e6bf","tid":209558,"uid":37661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:02:18.000Z","msg":"上次新聞咪講，意外原因係左右都企人。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】旺角朗豪坊的通天梯昨日下午發生恐怖「瀡滑梯」疑因扶手梯驅動鏈斷裝導致意外，上升中的扶手電梯突然反方向急速下行14秒，乘客如骨牌般人叠人跌下，香港電梯業總工會理事長謝景華指事故罕見及嚴重，從意外一刻片段可見大部份梯級都站有兩人負荷過重，而扶手電梯的安全裝置應會在倒後行時煞停電梯，但事件中的扶手梯仍持續下行一段時間才停下，機電署應徹查事故原因。<br />\n <br />\n促機電署檢討檢查次數<br />\n謝景華指近年多個大型商場都設橫跨數層樓的扶手電梯，方便市民，今次事故凸顯扶手梯的安全性，他指行內一般叫橫跨3層樓的扶手梯做天梯，這類扶手梯的制動及牽引裝置與一般一層樓高扶手梯相近，但因長度較長，需用較大動力，而且載重量亦較高。<br />\n<br />\n他補充，扶手梯倒後行是嚴重故障，扶手梯的驅動鏈用以牽引帶動梯級運行，現時有兩重安全系統預防，分別是電子感應截電系統及機械制動系統，當電子感應系統未有生效時，機械制動系統便會立即煞停，但從乘客如骨牌滾下歷時14秒的片段看，謝景華質疑當時制動系統並未生效。<br />\n他續稱這類天梯一般每級大約只可站一人，否則會負荷過重，而且設天梯商場人流極旺，為安全起見，機電署應檢討是否維持現行每兩周檢查一次，還是增加檢查次數。<br />\n<br />\n發生意外的通天梯是朗豪坊商場的室內扶手梯，朗豪坊於2004年開幕，商場樓高15層，共分兩段的通天梯連接4至8樓，及8至12樓，總長度達83米，是全港最長的無承托室內扶手梯，貫穿商場不同區域，是商場的一大特色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170326/19970367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170326%2F19970367&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3zM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=f1ca5bff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170326%2F19970367&h=f860003e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170326/19970367</a>"},{"pid":"3851f471ded86cee30d3337b9f7a5ebb8a00992d","tid":209558,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我連藍田同太古城嗰兩條都唔夠膽行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 細膽</blockquote><br />\n太古果條真心恐怖<br />\n<br />\n樓底已經矮 重要又長又斜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感覺好壓迫好辛苦"},{"pid":"96178673b58bb090de9b51703985a01151a3bbb3","tid":209558,"uid":83922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有調景嶺hkdi個條梯</blockquote><br />\n緊係唔行啦 夏天好多野昅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cb654f4bb3355f6e6f739c2fe66c3444c2b305","tid":209558,"uid":90083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:03:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我連藍田同太古城嗰兩條都唔夠膽行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 細膽</blockquote><br />\n太古果條真心恐怖<br />\n<br />\n樓底已經矮 重要又長又斜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感覺好壓迫好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n邊條？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fcef36ecf034aa63c